            <div class="description"><h3 style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Handheld Computers</h3>
<ul style="color: #666666;">
<li><strong>Improved inventory management</strong> – Real-time data collection for more accurate data and easier, faster cycle counting</li>
<li><strong>Increased visibility</strong> – Access to real-time-data enables better planning and faster decision making, and reduce risk of out-of-stock items</li>
<li><strong>Better accuracy</strong> – Best-in-class barcode scanning minimizes errors in picking, inventory management and more</li>
</ul></div>
            

                

                
