<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-13 dnd-section">
<div class="row-fluid ">
<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column" style="" data-widget-type="cell" data-x="0" data-w="12">

<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-14 dnd-row">
<div class="row-fluid ">
<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" style="" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" data-w="12">
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1713588882361" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module"> 


<div class="cnt-wit-tp-img-wrp dnd_padd widget_1713588882361 col4_row  unlock-more-benefits ">
  






  


  
  

  <div class="page-center theme_center">
    

<div class="top_sec noButton ">
  

    
    <div class="content_widget col8 ">
      

        
        <div class="top_content">
      <h2 style="line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center;">Industry-Specific Applications</h2>
<p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px;">Across the supply chain, enterprise tablets &amp; computers have become critical components to workflow efficiency. From retail storefronts, to delivery trucks and distribution centers, today’s mobile computers and rugged tablets have revolutionized efficiency, delivering automation and reliability businesses can count on.</p>
    </div>
    
  </div>
  

  

  

</div>


    <div class="bottom_row  ">
      <div class="splide__track"> 
        <div class="flex-row flex_row ">
          
          <div class="cnt-col splide__slide center_aln col4 ">
            <div class="inner_spacing  theme">
              
              
              <div class="tp-img-cnt">
                
                
                

                
                <h3 class="col-title">
                  Warehousing
                  </h3>
                  

                  
                  <div class="tp-img-cnt-inner">
                <p>In warehouses and distribution centers of all sizes, smart warehouse technologies like mobile computers streamline receiving, picking, put-away, cycle counting, and shipping. Real-time data capture minimizes errors and speeds up inventory turns. Wearable devices and vehicle-mounted computers allow workers to navigate hands-free while still in motion, improving safety and work speed.&nbsp;</p>
                
              </div>
              

              
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
        
          <div class="cnt-col splide__slide center_aln col4 ">
            <div class="inner_spacing  theme">
              
              
              <div class="tp-img-cnt">
                
                
                

                
                <h3 class="col-title">
                  Manufacturing
                  </h3>
                  

                  
                  <div class="tp-img-cnt-inner">
                <p>In factories and manufacturing facilities, mobile computing solutions enhance productivity by providing real-time access to production schedules, quality control checklists, and machine diagnostics. Operators and maintenance teams use rugged mobile computers and rugged tablets to report issues, receive alerts, and track work orders directly from the production floor. This minimizes downtime and ensures a more responsive and agile manufacturing process.</p>
                
              </div>
              

              
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
        
          <div class="cnt-col splide__slide center_aln col4 ">
            <div class="inner_spacing  theme">
              
              
              <div class="tp-img-cnt">
                
                
                

                
                <h3 class="col-title">
                  Transportation &amp; Logistics
                  </h3>
                  

                  
                  <div class="tp-img-cnt-inner">
                <p>Drivers rely on mobile devices for route navigation, and real-time communication with dispatch. Tablets with GPS and mobile data ensure visibility and traceability, and mobile computing is indispensable for tracking shipments, managing delivery routes, and maintaining clear communication between dispatchers and drivers. Rugged tablets and mobile computers enable electronic proof of delivery, GPS navigation, and real-time updates, improving delivery accuracy and customer satisfaction.&nbsp;</p>
                
              </div>
              

              
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
        
          <div class="cnt-col splide__slide center_aln col4 ">
            <div class="inner_spacing  theme">
              
              
              <div class="tp-img-cnt">
                
                
                

                
                <h3 class="col-title">
                  Retail
                  </h3>
                  

                  
                  <div class="tp-img-cnt-inner">
                <p>Enterprise mobile devices empower retail associates to locate items, check prices, and process transactions on the spot. This enhances customer experience and supports omnichannel fulfillment strategies. Mobile devices empower associates to assist customers more effectively with real-time product information, mobile point-of-sale capabilities, and inventory checks. Tablets also support tasks such as shelf audits, pricing updates, and stock replenishment.&nbsp;</p>
                
              </div>
              

              
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
        
          <div class="cnt-col splide__slide center_aln col4 ">
            <div class="inner_spacing  theme">
              
              
              <div class="tp-img-cnt">
                
                
                

                
                <h3 class="col-title">
                  Healthcare
                  </h3>
                  

                  
                  <div class="tp-img-cnt-inner">
                <p>Handheld mobile devices and tablets streamline healthcare workflows by enhancing mobility, efficiency, and patient care. These devices enable clinicians to access real-time patient records, medication data, and diagnostic tools at the point of care, reducing delays and minimizing errors. Their rugged, disinfectant-ready designs ensures reliability in demanding environments, where drops, spills, and frequent sanitization are common.&nbsp;</p>
                
              </div>
              

              
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
         
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  
</div>









































</div>



</div>

