<div class="row-fluid ">
<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell cell_17128895100135-padding dnd-column" style="" data-widget-type="cell" data-x="0" data-w="12">

<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-7 dnd-row">
<div class="row-fluid ">
<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" style="" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" data-w="12">
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_17128895100137" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module">  
<div class="dnd_padd accordion_wrap styleChanger show_active noImageNdParallax cm-accordion-2 module_17128895100137 " id="">
  






  


  
  


  <div class="page-center custom">

    

<div class="top_sec noButton ">
  

    
    <div class="content_widget col8 ">
      

        
        <div class="top_content">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    </div>
    
  </div>
  

  

  

</div>



    <div class="accord_outer">
      
      <div class="acc-item   ">
        <div class="acctitle  showctive_acc">
          <h4> 
          <span>What is a rugged mobile computer? </span>
          <div class="carrortwrap">
            
            <svg class="plus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="plus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>
            <svg class="minus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="minus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>            
          </div>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-content ">
          
          <div class="desc">
            <p>A rugged computer is a computer designed to operate reliably in harsh usage conditions. They must withstand strong vibrations, extreme temperatures, and wet or dusty conditions. They are purpose-built for these types of environments.</p>
          </div>
          
          
          

          
            </div>
          </div>

          
      <div class="acc-item   ">
        <div class="acctitle  showctive_acc">
          <h4> 
          <span>What makes a mobile device rugged?</span>
          <div class="carrortwrap">
            
            <svg class="plus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="plus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>
            <svg class="minus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="minus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>            
          </div>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-content ">
          
          <div class="desc">
            <p>Rugged mobile devices often feature reinforced casings, sunlight-readable displays, glove-compatible touchscreens, and specialized batteries for extreme temperatures. These features ensure uninterrupted performance across shifts and in various environments.</p>
          </div>
          
          
          

          
            </div>
          </div>

          
      <div class="acc-item   ">
        <div class="acctitle  showctive_acc">
          <h4> 
          <span>What are handheld devices? </span>
          <div class="carrortwrap">
            
            <svg class="plus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="plus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>
            <svg class="minus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="minus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>            
          </div>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-content ">
          
          <div class="desc">
            <p>A handheld device is any computing, electronic, or mechanical device that is small and portable enough to be held and used in one or both hands.</p>
          </div>
          
          
          

          
            </div>
          </div>

          
      <div class="acc-item   ">
        <div class="acctitle  showctive_acc">
          <h4> 
          <span>What is a rugged tablet? </span>
          <div class="carrortwrap">
            
            <svg class="plus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="plus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>
            <svg class="minus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="minus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>            
          </div>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-content ">
          
          <div class="desc">
            <p>A rugged tablet is a tablet designed to operate reliably in harsh usage conditions. They must withstand strong vibrations, extreme temperatures, and wet or dusty conditions. They are purpose-built for these types of environments.</p>
          </div>
          
          
          

          
            </div>
          </div>

          
      <div class="acc-item   ">
        <div class="acctitle  showctive_acc">
          <h4> 
          <span>What is a wearable device? </span>
          <div class="carrortwrap">
            
            <svg class="plus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="plus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>
            <svg class="minus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="minus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>            
          </div>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-content ">
          
          <div class="desc">
            <p>A wearable mobile device is designed to be worn on the body, allowing users to access and interact with information while keeping their hands free. These devices are built to be durable, secure, and easily integrated into enterprise systems, like warehouse management systems (WMS), enterprise resource planning (ERP), or manufacturing execution systems (MES).</p>
          </div>
          
          
          

          
            </div>
          </div>

          
      <div class="acc-item   ">
        <div class="acctitle  showctive_acc">
          <h4> 
          <span>What kind of support is available for Heartland mobile computers and tablets?</span>
          <div class="carrortwrap">
            
            <svg class="plus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="plus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>
            <svg class="minus" version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><g id="minus1_layer"><path d="M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></g></svg>            
          </div>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-content ">
          
          <div class="desc">
            <p>Heartland’s AlwaysOn suite of Mobile Device Management services can offload administrative burdens and helpdesk tickets related to your mobile technology hardware. From configuration to an integrated helpdesk, AlwaysOn manages the workload so your team can focus on what they do best.</p>
          </div>
          
          
          

          
            </div>
          </div>

          
        </div>
        


      </div>

      
      

















































































      
      

















































































      
      

















































































      
      

















































































      
      

















































































      
      




      

      





      
    </div>

    


    


    
    
    


    </div>

</div><!--end widget-span -->
